OL,3,CUK's first drug consumption room to
OL,4,Copen in Glasgow
OL,6,FThe first safe drug consumption room
OL,7,Fin the UK will open in Glasgow in
OL,8,FJanuary, the council has confirmed.
OL,10,FThe facility will allow drug users to
OL,11,Ftake illegal substances under medical
OL,12,Fsupervision with the hopes they will
OL,13,Fseek further support to tackle their
OL,14,Faddiction.
OL,16,FIt was hoped the facility would open
OL,17,Flast year, but final checks to the
OL,18,Fwater and ventilation systems pushed
OL,19,Fits opening back.
