OL,3,CUK's first drug consumption room to
OL,4,Copen in Glasgow
OL,6,FLocated on Hunter Street in the city's
OL,7,Feast end, the facility ` known as the
OL,8,FThistle ` will open on January 13 and
OL,9,Foperate between 9am and 9pm, 365 days
OL,10,Fa year.
OL,12,FCouncillor Allan Casey, convener for
OL,13,Faddiction services at Glasgow City
OL,14,FCouncil, said: "We have been pushing
OL,15,Ffor a safer drug consumption facility
OL,16,Ffor some time.
OL,18,F"It's a welcome relief to know we can
OL,19,Ffinally have people in to access the
OL,20,Fservice and support available within
OL,21,Fthe Thistle.
