OL,6,F"We know from all the other safer drug
OL,7,Fconsumption rooms in operation across
OL,8,Fthe world that they do make a
OL,9,Fdifference."
OL,11,FScotland has the highest number of
OL,12,Fdrug-related deaths in Europe.
OL,14,FFigures in August showed that the
OL,15,Fnumber of people who died in Scotland
OL,16,Fdue to drugs increased by 12% between
OL,17,F2022 and 2023.
