OL,3,CUK's first drug consumption room to
OL,4,Copen in Glasgow
OL,6,FWhile the idea of a drugs consumption
OL,7,Froom was first proposed in 2016
OL,8,Ffollowing an HIV outbreak in the city,
OL,9,Fits development was embroiled in years
OL,10,Fof political wrangling between the
OL,11,FScottish and UK governments.
OL,13,FBut in 2023, Scotland's Lord Advocate
OL,14,FDorothy Bain KC announced it would not
OL,15,Fbe "in the public interest" to
OL,16,Fprosecute people using such a facility.
